commit_message: improved bar graphs (adding labels, axes, titles etc)
added plots showing diff between high and low scoring group
added a few details to homology files
added function to normalize, modified count_lower_higher function so user can set thresholds to different values
fixed an error in the dataset
added code that calculates Pearson correlation coefficient for parameter scores and experimental inhibition values, and plots them
added to sirna dataset analysis section
updated homology module, added sequences file
add updated datasets C and D
made homology module more user-friendly, added clearer structure
Added explanation for taqman probe code
structured and improved code that checks whether a taqman probe has cross species reactivity, made it more  userfriendly
new scripts that employ the sirna scoring code on published sirna datasets to see which parameters actually  differ significantly between empirically determined good and bad sirnas
added function that finds sirna targets which lie in homologous regions
lists of matches are now saved following computation
added functions that retrieve sense and antisense for any list of positions on mrna sequence
fixed mapping onto mrna target regions
updated oligowalk and sfold result links
added compatibility for input sequences larger than 10k bp
